WEBVTT

01:45.666 --> 01:48.583
Let me stop you right there.
My name's Ollie.

01:48.666 --> 01:52.000
It might surprise you,
but this isn't the worst day of my life.

01:52.666 --> 01:54.416
Oh, no, no, no, no, no.

01:54.500 --> 01:58.250
That happened a long time ago,
when I was a kid.

01:59.041 --> 02:00.708
As long as I can remember,

02:00.791 --> 02:03.833
curiosity has always
seemed to get the better of me.

05:50.750 --> 05:53.625
Oh, hey, Dad. Um… Uh…

05:53.708 --> 05:55.166
Thirsty?

05:55.250 --> 05:58.791
Ollie, you never trust any other creature.

05:58.875 --> 06:00.375
My little Ollie-kins!

06:00.458 --> 06:03.416
I made you a new harvest hat.

06:03.500 --> 06:04.708
He went off island.

06:04.791 --> 06:06.000
You went off island?

06:06.083 --> 06:08.458
Mom, you wouldn't believe what I saw.

06:08.541 --> 06:10.250
It was incredible.

06:10.333 --> 06:12.833
There was these leaves with eyes.

06:12.916 --> 06:17.625
Oh, oh, and this giant fish
with rainbow scales smiled at me.

06:17.708 --> 06:19.208
Really? Big rainbow fish?

06:19.291 --> 06:21.875
I don't care! You don't go off island.

06:21.958 --> 06:24.708
-But why?
-Because it's dangerous, that's why.

06:24.791 --> 06:26.083
We're worried about you.

06:26.166 --> 06:29.375
I don't see what the big deal is.
I was just exploring.

06:29.458 --> 06:32.333
Son, the Pookoo
aren't supposed to be curious.

06:32.416 --> 06:33.416
What's our motto?

06:33.500 --> 06:37.833
-"Hide today, alive tomorrow."
-Exactly.

06:37.916 --> 06:41.000
That's why we're blessed
with our Pookoo nose,

06:41.083 --> 06:44.083
so that we can smell threats
and stay away.

06:44.166 --> 06:46.958
We smell everything,
but not everything is a threat.

06:47.041 --> 06:49.583
That's it. I'm telling him the Tale.

06:49.666 --> 06:50.750
Caloo! No

06:50.833 --> 06:51.916
Wait. The Tale?

06:52.000 --> 06:55.666
As in the Tale the Tale?
I want to hear it.

06:55.750 --> 06:59.416
He's too young to hear about the… wolf.
He'll have nightmares.

06:59.500 --> 07:01.791
I won't. Lodd's parents told him.

07:01.875 --> 07:05.250
I don't think we should be taking advice
from Lodd's parents.

07:05.333 --> 07:07.083
Oh my goodness, come on.

07:07.166 --> 07:09.916
-What the--
-He needs to know!

07:10.000 --> 07:11.416
Grandma?

07:11.500 --> 07:16.791
With the wind whistling eerily
through the hallows,

07:16.875 --> 07:22.541
the dark one came
on a black and cloudless night.

07:22.625 --> 07:28.375
The great destroyer who ignited hellfire

07:28.458 --> 07:30.541
torched the Valley.

07:30.625 --> 07:32.708
Oh wow. This is gonna be awesome.

07:32.791 --> 07:35.000
You want to dial it back, please?

07:35.083 --> 07:36.125
No!

07:36.625 --> 07:39.916
It all started a long time ago

07:40.000 --> 07:43.625
when the Valley
was a very different place.

07:44.291 --> 07:48.250
The Pookoo didn't always
live on an island like we do now.

07:48.791 --> 07:51.833
They lived amongst the other animals…

07:51.916 --> 07:56.833
…in fear of the ferocious wolf
who stalked the Valley.

08:00.958 --> 08:05.125
But then everything changed.

08:05.208 --> 08:09.416
Into the Valley came a creature so huge,

08:09.500 --> 08:14.958
the Dzo, the magnificent walking orchards.

08:15.041 --> 08:20.916
In their vast wisdom and kindness,
the Dzo offered the creatures a gift.

08:21.000 --> 08:24.625
From their branches
grew a magical glowing pod,

08:24.708 --> 08:30.666
which had the incredible power
to transform one creature into another.

08:36.916 --> 08:41.625
The pods gave them
the ability to understand each other,

08:41.708 --> 08:44.916
which brought them all together.

08:45.666 --> 08:47.500
But the wolf,

08:47.583 --> 08:51.000
bitter that he had lost control
of the Valley,

08:51.083 --> 08:53.125
despised this new way,

08:53.208 --> 08:59.625
so he stole the Dzo's gift
to become a monster.

09:00.416 --> 09:05.208
To become the Firewolf!

09:05.291 --> 09:09.250
In order to destroy the pods,
he attacked the Dzo!

09:09.958 --> 09:12.583
He slayed the first four!

09:14.666 --> 09:17.625
Then drove the rest away.

09:25.166 --> 09:26.958
Causing a rock slide,

09:28.958 --> 09:30.375
which created a dam.

09:37.583 --> 09:42.166
He banished the remaining Dzo
outside the Valley forever.

09:43.375 --> 09:47.708
Without the Dzo,
he plunged the creatures of the Valley

09:47.791 --> 09:52.875
back to a life of fear and mistrust.

09:54.666 --> 10:01.666
And the Firewolf still rules the Valley
to this very day.

10:04.375 --> 10:06.666
Hmm? Pretty good stuff, huh?

10:07.666 --> 10:08.666
Eh.

10:08.750 --> 10:11.458
"Eh"? What do you mean, "Eh"?

10:11.541 --> 10:14.000
Where's the blood and guts? The gore?

10:14.083 --> 10:17.541
What if the Firewolf
rips apart the Pinecone Hedgehogs

10:17.625 --> 10:19.333
and feasts on their entrails?

10:19.416 --> 10:21.666
That would be awesome.

10:23.708 --> 10:25.875
You know what? That's your son.

10:25.958 --> 10:29.541
We love you. We just want you to be safe.

10:29.625 --> 10:32.125
-I know.
-Look around, kiddo.

10:32.208 --> 10:34.416
This place, these Pookoo,

10:34.500 --> 10:37.916
it's the one thing
you don't have to be afraid of.

10:38.000 --> 10:40.666
That's why we're celebrating,

10:40.750 --> 10:43.375
to give thanks for the piplet harvest.

10:43.458 --> 10:46.791
We are very fortunate to have all of this.

11:01.208 --> 11:04.708
Ready, set, pass the piplet!

11:22.291 --> 11:24.250
A Javan?

11:32.916 --> 11:35.500
I know we're not supposed to be curious.

14:01.708 --> 14:02.958
Ollie!

14:03.791 --> 14:06.208
I can smell you around here somewhere.

14:06.291 --> 14:07.958
Hey, where are you?

14:09.291 --> 14:11.875
Hey, Dad, don't worry. It's not dangerous.

14:11.958 --> 14:13.625
It's smart. Look.

14:13.708 --> 14:15.125
I taught it the trick.

14:16.875 --> 14:18.250
I taught it how to eat.

15:07.541 --> 15:08.750
Ollie.

15:10.041 --> 15:12.000
What have you done?

15:18.583 --> 15:22.125
Yup, that was it. Worst day of my life.

15:22.750 --> 15:25.875
What's that saying?
Curiosity killed the cat.

15:25.958 --> 15:27.625
I don't know what a cat is,

15:27.708 --> 15:30.791
but my curiosity
definitely doomed the Pookoo.

15:44.000 --> 15:46.291
The Javan, they're eating everything.

15:46.375 --> 15:48.625
There's more every year.

15:48.708 --> 15:52.750
-Take, take, take. That's all they do.
-But what about the emergency rations?

15:52.833 --> 15:54.166
They're gone.

15:54.250 --> 15:56.625
The storage is nearly empty.

15:56.708 --> 16:00.125
How are we gonna make it
through the winter?

16:00.208 --> 16:04.125
We need to find more piplets or… or…

16:04.208 --> 16:05.541
Or what?

16:07.500 --> 16:08.833
We starve.

16:24.750 --> 16:26.166
Uh, Dad.

16:26.250 --> 16:29.416
Hey, Dad. I was
up on the surface with my leaf camo.

16:31.125 --> 16:34.375
And I… And I was able to find this.

16:45.500 --> 16:48.458
Why did I have to feed that Javan?

16:48.541 --> 16:52.416
Why? Huh? What is wrong with me?

18:00.625 --> 18:01.833
It works?

18:02.375 --> 18:04.291
Dad, it works!

18:04.375 --> 18:05.750
Everybody, listen!

18:06.291 --> 18:09.541
I found the solution!

18:10.375 --> 18:11.750
Yes, yes, yes, yes!

18:11.833 --> 18:13.833
Ah, okay.

18:19.333 --> 18:21.000
Well, look who it is.

18:21.083 --> 18:22.166
A hero.

18:22.250 --> 18:23.791
Come on, let's go.

18:24.833 --> 18:27.041
Big dumb sack of feathers.
Come and get me.

18:27.125 --> 18:29.750
What are you waiting for? Come on!

18:29.833 --> 18:31.000
Come on and get me!

19:22.000 --> 19:23.583
Glowing pod?

19:24.250 --> 19:26.000
From… the Tale?

19:26.500 --> 19:27.875
It's true.

19:27.958 --> 19:31.333
No. Nope, nope, nope, nope.

19:31.416 --> 19:33.750
We're not doing this. Nope.

19:33.833 --> 19:36.250
Don't need magic glowing pod thingies.

19:36.333 --> 19:40.416
This is all your fault, you stupid Javan!

19:53.333 --> 19:55.333
Ollie!

19:56.625 --> 19:57.833
Come on.

19:57.916 --> 20:00.166
Ollie! Hello?

20:01.291 --> 20:02.541
Ollie!

20:02.625 --> 20:04.791
My head.

20:04.875 --> 20:05.916
Ollie!

20:07.166 --> 20:08.291
Is that you?

20:08.375 --> 20:10.541
Yeah. I'm down here!

20:10.625 --> 20:12.958
He's here! Guys, I found him.

20:13.041 --> 20:16.500
He's in the hole!
He is in a really, really dark hole.

20:16.583 --> 20:19.416
-What are you doing there?
-Are you stuck, honey?

20:19.500 --> 20:22.458
What's hurt?
Your ankle, leg, arm, ribs, back?

20:22.541 --> 20:25.916
-Don't tell me it's your head!
-No, it's not.

20:26.000 --> 20:28.333
I just feel a little weird.

20:28.416 --> 20:29.875
Then come out already.

20:29.958 --> 20:31.625
I'm coming.

20:39.541 --> 20:40.625
Javan!

20:40.708 --> 20:43.333
What? What? Where? Where?

20:43.833 --> 20:45.666
Wait, wait. Whoa, I'm a…

20:45.750 --> 20:48.166
No, no, no. I'm a--

20:48.250 --> 20:49.500
Javan!

20:49.583 --> 20:51.916
No, Mama! Help. Help me!

20:52.000 --> 20:53.333
Ma, it's me!

20:54.958 --> 20:55.958
Ollie?

20:57.458 --> 20:58.583
Help me.

20:59.083 --> 21:00.750
I'm scared, Ma.

21:02.083 --> 21:06.750
Ollie's voice… coming from that bird?

21:07.458 --> 21:09.208
Well, that means…

21:09.708 --> 21:12.083
The bird ate Ollie!

21:12.166 --> 21:13.875
The Javan ate Ollie!

21:18.708 --> 21:21.041
No! Ollie!

21:21.875 --> 21:24.083
-Calli!
-The Javan ate Ollie!

21:38.000 --> 21:39.208
Whoa!

22:10.583 --> 22:12.291
Pookoo Island?

22:12.875 --> 22:14.291
Ah!

22:15.916 --> 22:16.916
Whoa!

22:17.958 --> 22:19.791
Ah!

22:35.500 --> 22:38.208
Javan! Javan! Javan!

22:47.833 --> 22:48.916
Hello!

22:50.541 --> 22:52.291
Ah! Ah! Ah!

22:55.541 --> 22:57.916
Get back! Get… Get away from me!

22:58.416 --> 23:00.500
Wait, wait, wait!

23:02.416 --> 23:04.500
-Uh, Ivy?
-Stay back!

23:04.583 --> 23:07.291
-Yes, Lily?
-Does he seem a little off?

23:07.375 --> 23:10.333
A little? Look what you did to him, Ivy.

23:10.416 --> 23:12.166
Get back, you!

23:12.250 --> 23:14.416
Violet, stop being so dramatic.

23:14.500 --> 23:15.833
He's fine.

23:15.916 --> 23:18.541
Hey there, big guy. How you doing?

23:18.625 --> 23:21.583
Stay back. Hey, you, stay back. Stay back.

23:21.666 --> 23:24.083
That's an odd way to say thank you.
I saved your life.

23:24.166 --> 23:25.416
Uh, we saved you.

23:25.500 --> 23:30.458
If by "we," you mean me, all by myself,
without any help from you, as usual,

23:30.541 --> 23:32.791
then, yes, we saved you.

23:32.875 --> 23:36.000
Stay back! Don't you move.
You. And you, you!

23:36.083 --> 23:37.208
I will use this!

23:37.291 --> 23:39.166
Let's put the stick down.

23:39.250 --> 23:41.458
Wow, you broke his brain.

23:41.541 --> 23:43.916
I did not break his brain.

23:44.000 --> 23:47.708
Hey there.
My name is Ivy. These are my sisters.

23:47.791 --> 23:50.666
Um, we can actually introduce ourselves.

23:50.750 --> 23:51.958
-I'm Violet.
-She's Violet.

23:52.041 --> 23:53.041
-She's Lily.
-Hi!

23:53.625 --> 23:57.500
You're just going to need
a teeny bit of medical attention,

23:57.583 --> 23:59.833
so I'm gonna take you to Javan Rock.

24:00.541 --> 24:02.833
Huh? Javan Rock?

24:02.916 --> 24:04.416
Yes. Home, there.

24:04.500 --> 24:07.291
I'm not going to Javan Rock.
That's not my home!

24:07.375 --> 24:08.875
Okay, buddy. Easy.

24:08.958 --> 24:12.041
Javan Rock has
everything we need to fix you up.

24:12.125 --> 24:14.500
-Trust me on this.
-Trust you? Trust you?

24:22.791 --> 24:23.791
That's hilarious.

24:23.875 --> 24:26.833
Maybe the fall knocked his hearing around.

24:26.916 --> 24:31.208
Do you understand me?

24:31.291 --> 24:36.208
Oh, I understand. I understand just fine
what you and your cunning, thieving…

24:36.291 --> 24:38.250
I… Wait, wait, wait. I…

24:38.333 --> 24:40.250
I understand you.

24:40.333 --> 24:43.583
How can I understand you?

24:44.083 --> 24:45.541
Because I'm trapped.

24:45.625 --> 24:48.750
It's because I'm trapped
inside the body of a Javan!

24:48.833 --> 24:51.291
Get these feathers off me! Get 'em off!

24:52.250 --> 24:54.625
Get these feathers off me!

24:54.708 --> 24:57.250
Oh no, he's gone. What did we do?

24:57.333 --> 25:00.000
-We? You mean what did she do?
-I'm stuck!

25:00.083 --> 25:01.375
Not helping!

25:01.458 --> 25:04.000
I'm stuck in here! Help! Somebody help me!

25:04.083 --> 25:06.625
Help you? Help me!

25:06.708 --> 25:09.791
I'm rolling dung here!
You gonna get out of my way?

25:09.875 --> 25:11.250
You can talk too?

25:11.333 --> 25:14.500
Yeah, that's right, genius,
and I'm talking to you.

25:14.583 --> 25:16.125
Now get outta here. Move it.

25:16.208 --> 25:18.125
Would you stop dawdling?

25:18.208 --> 25:20.333
How long do I gotta wait for this dung?

25:20.416 --> 25:24.791
Now you're gonna bust my chops too?
First, this idiot, and now you!

25:24.875 --> 25:26.333
You don't have to yell.

25:26.416 --> 25:29.625
How would I know?
They look like little dirt balls to me.

25:29.708 --> 25:33.333
Um, Ivy, he's talking to bugs now.

25:33.416 --> 25:37.458
About dung. Ivy, he's talking about dung.
Tell him what you did.

25:37.541 --> 25:42.708
-Mmm, you mean heroically save his life?
-I think she means the, um, other thing?

25:42.791 --> 25:45.375
Other things! Plural!

25:45.458 --> 25:47.250
What are y'all talking about?

25:47.333 --> 25:50.125
Okay, fine. When I was rescuing you,

25:50.208 --> 25:52.541
I might have overestimated
your swimming ability.

25:55.416 --> 25:59.208
-Wait. You dragged my head underwater?
-And?

25:59.291 --> 26:03.541
And then I might have accidentally
brushed up against a pebble.

26:06.333 --> 26:07.625
You did what?

26:07.708 --> 26:09.208
There was also…

26:11.666 --> 26:13.416
Okay, enough!

26:13.500 --> 26:17.625
You were slippery. And quite heavy.
And I was a little shorthanded!

26:17.708 --> 26:19.458
Wait, wait, wait. It's you!

26:19.541 --> 26:22.208
You're that hero Javan
that knocked me into the pit.

26:22.291 --> 26:25.583
Yes! I am a hero.

26:25.666 --> 26:28.416
Thanks to me, you're safe now
from the angry little rat.

26:28.500 --> 26:30.875
That angry little rat is me!

26:30.958 --> 26:33.041
And I'm not a rat, I'm a Pookoo!

26:33.750 --> 26:35.833
Pookoo? What's a Pookoo?

26:35.916 --> 26:39.291
He's making up words now.
You still don't think you broke his brain?

26:39.375 --> 26:41.625
-I did not break his brain!
-She broke your brain.

26:41.708 --> 26:45.166
At most, you are mildly concussed,
which is why we have to take you home.

26:45.250 --> 26:47.833
You're using that word again, "home."
What do you mean?

26:47.916 --> 26:50.291
-Javan Rock.
-Javan Rock is not my home!

26:52.250 --> 26:54.166
-What is that?
-No time for questions.

26:54.250 --> 26:55.875
She doesn't like being questioned.

26:55.958 --> 26:58.125
I don't mind!
There's just nothing to question,

26:58.208 --> 26:59.875
so do what I say and fly!

26:59.958 --> 27:02.333
I can't fly. Get off me!

27:07.166 --> 27:08.875
-Ivy…
-Okay, plan B.

27:08.958 --> 27:11.583
If it can't smell him, it can't eat him.

27:11.666 --> 27:14.583
Lily, hold him down.
Violet, smear him with dung.

27:14.666 --> 27:17.208
-What?!
-I am not touching that stuff.

27:17.291 --> 27:21.125
Would it really kill you
to follow my lead just once?

27:21.208 --> 27:22.958
Ugh, you're so bossy!

27:25.416 --> 27:28.166
No, no! Not like that! Like this.

27:28.250 --> 27:30.958
See how the feathers are caking up?

27:31.041 --> 27:34.000
Just jam the dung
all the way down into the quill.

27:34.083 --> 27:37.000
Aw, so cute. He's like a little dung baby.

27:37.083 --> 27:40.541
Get to Javan Rock.
Lily, you're in charge while I'm gone.

27:40.625 --> 27:41.541
-Yay!
-What?

27:41.625 --> 27:43.458
-I'm older!
-It's not about who's oldest.

27:43.541 --> 27:45.458
-Since when?
-Since I'm oldest.

27:45.541 --> 27:47.583
Now do what I told Lily to tell you to do!

27:47.666 --> 27:51.166
-Sodding tyrant.
-Good luck, dung baby!

27:52.416 --> 27:54.125
Come on! Hurry!

27:54.208 --> 27:56.583
Stay put. Trust me on this.

27:57.458 --> 27:59.083
Huh, trust you?

28:09.166 --> 28:10.750
Firewolf?

28:22.458 --> 28:23.833
Dad was right?

28:26.250 --> 28:29.583
Stupid pods and stupid birds.

28:29.666 --> 28:32.291
Stupid transformations.

28:33.000 --> 28:34.000
Ew.

28:38.958 --> 28:40.458
Hi!

28:41.541 --> 28:42.541
Ah!

28:43.250 --> 28:45.750
-What you doing?
-Shh, there's a Firewolf around!

28:45.833 --> 28:47.500
Firewolf? Where?

28:48.125 --> 28:52.041
-What's a Firewolf?
-Shh! It's gone. I think.

28:57.833 --> 29:01.333
Wait. I know you.
Didn't we meet a long time ago?

29:01.416 --> 29:03.333
-Yes.
-I knew it!

29:03.416 --> 29:06.041
One moment ago
counts as a long time, right?

29:06.125 --> 29:08.416
-No.
-Oh, then no.

29:08.500 --> 29:11.625
But I'm the only Boogle
in the lake, so yes!

29:12.500 --> 29:13.500
Who are you?

29:13.583 --> 29:15.041
Yeah, about that… Um…

29:15.125 --> 29:17.916
It's hard to explain.
I'm in the wrong body.

29:18.000 --> 29:20.041
Oh. Wrong body.

29:20.125 --> 29:21.916
Sounds fun. How'd that happen?

29:22.000 --> 29:23.166
I fell into this pit,

29:23.250 --> 29:26.166
and there was this glowing pod
that my grandmother told me about,

29:26.250 --> 29:27.250
from the Dzo.

29:27.333 --> 29:30.958
These walking orchard things
from a long time ago.

29:31.583 --> 29:34.083
Why am I bothering?
It doesn't make any sense.

29:34.708 --> 29:36.875
Was it a pretty glowing pod?

29:36.958 --> 29:38.125
Yeah.

29:38.208 --> 29:40.416
Yep. I've seen those.

29:40.500 --> 29:42.875
You have? You know where another one is?

29:42.958 --> 29:44.333
Mmm, yeah, I do.

29:44.416 --> 29:46.750
See that? It's right through the grove.

29:46.833 --> 29:48.916
Look for the big round dead tree.

29:49.000 --> 29:52.041
Got it. Glowing pod. Big round dead tree.

29:52.125 --> 29:55.041
-Thanks! Wait, what's your name?
-Boogle. What's yours?

29:55.125 --> 29:56.541
Ollie. Thanks, Boogle!

29:56.625 --> 29:59.291
Big round dead tree, glowing pod.

30:00.041 --> 30:03.000
-Big round dead tree, glowing pod.
-Um, hey there.

30:03.083 --> 30:07.291
Buddy! Did we forget the whole part
when I clearly said "stay put"?

30:07.375 --> 30:11.416
Turn me back to a Pookoo. Find the tree.
Glowing pod. Turn me back to a Pookoo.

30:11.500 --> 30:14.833
-Smiling fish told me.
-Smiling fish. Magic glowing pods.

30:14.916 --> 30:18.125
-A fish that was smiling told me. Whoa!
-It's getting worse.

30:24.125 --> 30:25.291
Okay, stop!

30:25.375 --> 30:27.333
You're gonna hurt yourself again.

30:27.416 --> 30:29.666
What do you need?

30:29.750 --> 30:31.916
I… I need that pod.

30:34.125 --> 30:37.666
I… I need that pod to turn back, okay?

30:37.750 --> 30:39.375
Into a Pookoo. A Pookoo.

30:39.458 --> 30:43.250
When you get this magic pod,
promise you'll come to Javan Rock?

30:43.333 --> 30:45.666
-Yeah, sure, whatever.
-Okay.

30:46.166 --> 30:48.541
Here's your precious pod.

30:48.625 --> 30:49.625
No, don't touch it!

30:49.708 --> 30:52.916
-So you can turn back into a Pookoo…
-No, please! Stop!

30:53.000 --> 30:56.333
…the strange creature you made up,
so we can get back to Javan Rock.

30:56.416 --> 30:58.166
No!

30:58.250 --> 31:00.416
No. Now, you promised.

31:01.458 --> 31:04.708
Wait, what is that smell?
Why does everything smell so much?

31:04.791 --> 31:07.041
No, no, no… Please, no.

31:08.583 --> 31:12.416
Ah! Where are my beautiful feathers?
Where are my beautiful wings?

31:12.500 --> 31:16.375
Oh, what are these
disgusting little claws?

31:16.916 --> 31:19.958
-What did you do?!
-Wait, wait, wait, no. Excuse me.

31:20.041 --> 31:21.458
What did I do?

31:21.541 --> 31:23.708
You took my pod and became a Pookoo.

31:23.791 --> 31:27.708
Pod? Pookoo?
Wait a second. I didn't break your brain?

31:27.791 --> 31:30.750
-No!
-Oh, I knew it. Take that, Violet.

31:30.833 --> 31:33.208
Why did you have to touch the pod? Why?!

31:33.291 --> 31:35.125
Why didn't you tell me not to?

31:35.208 --> 31:36.208
-I did!
-When?

31:36.291 --> 31:37.916
Literally before you touched it.

31:38.000 --> 31:40.583
Well, you obviously
didn't explain it very well

31:40.666 --> 31:43.333
because if you had,
I would have understood it.

31:43.416 --> 31:47.875
You know what? I'm done. I'm done!
I'm not wasting another second on you

31:47.958 --> 31:50.375
because all you've done is ruin my life!

31:50.458 --> 31:52.291
Oh, what is your problem?

31:52.375 --> 31:56.041
You… You nut… You nut cake!

31:56.125 --> 32:00.875
I don't know why you're so upset.
It is not like any of this is my fault.

32:00.958 --> 32:02.791
Any? All. All your fault!

32:02.875 --> 32:05.166
-Name one thing.
-You threw me into that pit.

32:05.250 --> 32:10.083
Wait, you were the angry little rat
blinding the Javan.

32:10.166 --> 32:13.333
I keep telling you I'm not a rat.
I'm a Pookoo!

32:13.416 --> 32:15.416
Pookoo is a really stupid name,
by the way.

32:15.500 --> 32:18.375
-You should've workshopped that more.
-It is not!

32:18.458 --> 32:22.541
I mean, do you guys realize
it's got "poo" in the name?

32:22.625 --> 32:26.708
I thought I hated you before, but now…

32:26.791 --> 32:28.291
-You love me?
-No.

32:28.375 --> 32:30.708
Oh, don't be ridiculous. I'm wonderful!

32:32.166 --> 32:34.708
-Goodbye.
-Hey! Where do you think you're going?

32:34.791 --> 32:36.250
-Nowhere.
-I don't believe you.

32:36.333 --> 32:38.083
-I don't care.
-You're up to something.

32:38.166 --> 32:40.208
You know how to find another pod.

32:40.291 --> 32:41.500
-No.
-You're lying.

32:41.583 --> 32:43.875
-I'm not.
-Fine. You won't mind if I follow you.

32:43.958 --> 32:45.125
-Stop.
-Sorry, buster.

32:45.208 --> 32:47.541
But from now on, I am your ride or die.

32:47.625 --> 32:48.916
I choose die.

32:54.416 --> 32:56.666
Wait. Boogle, Boogle! Great. Great.

32:56.750 --> 32:59.708
Hey, Ollie, did you find the pod?

32:59.791 --> 33:03.458
-No. It was stolen. Too much to explain.
-Excuse me! I did not steal it!

33:03.541 --> 33:05.583
Ooh! Who's your friend, Ollie?

33:05.666 --> 33:08.791
Nobody. She's nobody.
Quick. Tell me where to find another pod.

33:08.875 --> 33:11.416
-You know, I do not appreciate--
-Hi, Nobody.

33:12.875 --> 33:14.583
Boogle fish… talk?

33:14.666 --> 33:17.750
-They do? Where?
-Stupid question. Yes, they can talk.

33:17.833 --> 33:19.875
-You've been talking to him, right?
-Right.

33:19.958 --> 33:22.583
But I just didn't
put it together until now.

33:22.666 --> 33:25.458
-Because you're not very smart.
-Please. I'm brilliant.

33:25.541 --> 33:29.500
Hello, Boogle!

33:29.583 --> 33:32.541
-Why are you talking like that?
-I want him to understand.

33:32.625 --> 33:35.833
He understands you just fine.
Unfortunately, we all understand you.

33:35.916 --> 33:39.708
Can you tell me

33:39.791 --> 33:44.125
where another pod is?

33:44.208 --> 33:47.166
No. Don't trust her. She's a Javan.
They're all liars and thieves.

33:47.250 --> 33:49.750
Well, all Pookoos are jealous,
petty little rodents.

33:49.833 --> 33:54.041
Oh, when I get that pod, I can't wait
to drive all of you off my island.

33:54.125 --> 33:57.041
Hey, hey. There's enough pods
for both of you.

33:57.125 --> 33:58.250
I've seen 'em.

34:00.666 --> 34:04.375
I've been alone my whole life.

34:04.458 --> 34:08.458
Well, ever since
the great rock slide flooded the Valley.

34:08.541 --> 34:12.625
So I've had a lot of time
to swim around and look at stuff.

34:12.708 --> 34:15.000
Wow. The stuff I've seen.

34:15.083 --> 34:17.083
Trees, shells, rocks,

34:17.166 --> 34:19.791
scary rocks, not-so-scary rocks…

34:19.875 --> 34:22.166
Yeah, okay, whatever. Scary rocks.

34:22.250 --> 34:23.458
What about the pods?

34:23.541 --> 34:25.041
From what I've seen,

34:25.125 --> 34:28.541
the pretty glowy pods
are only on an old Dzo.

34:29.791 --> 34:30.958
The Dzo.

34:31.041 --> 34:34.000
-The great walking orchards?
-That's right.

34:34.083 --> 34:36.208
The Javan used to live on their branches.

34:36.958 --> 34:39.000
But… they disappeared.

34:39.083 --> 34:41.458
Yeah, all but four dead ones.

34:41.541 --> 34:44.000
Sorry. I know
it's a little scary to say "dead,"

34:44.083 --> 34:46.625
but I don't know
how else to say not alive.

34:46.708 --> 34:50.250
-Not living, dead ones.
-Okay, can we just stay on the pods?

34:50.333 --> 34:53.416
Please. Where is
the next closest dead Dzo?

34:53.500 --> 34:56.416
Oh yeah, that would be
by the Great Waterfall.

34:56.500 --> 34:58.333
Yeah, it's a big one.

34:58.416 --> 35:01.625
The Dzo, the waterfall. They're both big.

35:02.458 --> 35:04.666
Where is this great waterfall?

35:04.750 --> 35:07.708
It's across the Valley,
way beyond those cliffs.

35:07.791 --> 35:11.208
Hey, there was something
I was gonna bring up,

35:11.291 --> 35:14.541
but I don't know how you would feel if…

35:15.750 --> 35:16.750
Ollie?

35:18.000 --> 35:19.083
Nobody?

35:19.750 --> 35:21.291
Anybody?

35:25.416 --> 35:26.541
Here we go.

35:33.041 --> 35:34.875
Why are you doing it that way?

35:34.958 --> 35:38.250
Look at these paws. How is anyone
supposed to climb with these?

35:38.333 --> 35:40.333
They're called wings. That's why we fly.

35:40.416 --> 35:42.125
-I don't fly.
-You could if you tried.

35:42.208 --> 35:43.958
Even baby Javans can fly.

35:44.041 --> 35:46.541
What am I supposed to do?
Just raise my wings and--

35:57.875 --> 35:59.166
Stupid wings.

35:59.250 --> 36:00.708
You can't dig.

36:00.791 --> 36:02.250
You can't grab things.

36:02.333 --> 36:04.250
You can't climb. This is--

36:04.333 --> 36:06.666
-They're completely useless.
-You cut that out.

36:06.750 --> 36:08.791
You are a majestic creature.

36:08.875 --> 36:10.375
Me, on the other hand,

36:10.458 --> 36:13.958
I'm short, hairy, pretty much
everything in the Valley wants to eat me.

36:14.041 --> 36:17.041
Don't flatter yourself.
I bet you taste terrible.

36:18.458 --> 36:20.291
-Quick, get the dung!
-No time!

36:20.375 --> 36:23.625
Smear me with the little dirt balls.
Turn me into a dung baby!

36:30.916 --> 36:34.458
Dad? Dad? Where are you?

36:34.541 --> 36:37.125
Wait, is that a baby Firewolf?

36:37.208 --> 36:38.916
Where did you go?

36:39.000 --> 36:40.458
Wolves talk?

36:40.541 --> 36:43.208
Everything can talk
once you touch a pod. Keep up.

36:43.291 --> 36:45.583
Poor thing's lost. Aw.

36:45.666 --> 36:47.666
-He just needs some help.
-Aw, I know.

36:47.750 --> 36:50.875
And then watch as it calls
its friends to ambush you

36:50.958 --> 36:53.291
and ruins your life forever.

36:53.375 --> 36:56.625
Okay, that's oddly specific.

36:58.000 --> 37:00.666
-Hey, what's that smell?
-Would you just be quiet?

37:00.750 --> 37:03.000
No. Oh, something really smells here.

37:03.083 --> 37:06.125
Shh! That thing's dad
is out there somewhere.

37:06.208 --> 37:08.250
He's right here.

37:15.875 --> 37:18.791
There you are. What are you doing?

37:18.875 --> 37:20.500
Looking for our prey.

37:20.583 --> 37:22.750
You mean the ones getting away?

37:27.375 --> 37:29.583
Fly! Embrace your Javan body!

37:29.666 --> 37:32.875
-Flap, Ollie!
-Shut it! I'm trying to run here!

37:39.041 --> 37:40.250
-Watch out!
-Whoa!

37:47.791 --> 37:49.541
That was almost like flying.

38:00.166 --> 38:03.000
-Run into the cave!
-What do you think I'm doing?

38:08.916 --> 38:12.041
Why are…
Why aren't they following us in here?

38:13.375 --> 38:14.375
Whoa!

38:18.875 --> 38:21.583
Maybe it's because of that awful stench.

38:21.666 --> 38:23.166
What does it smell like?

38:23.250 --> 38:24.916
Hmm. I don't know. Ugh.

38:25.000 --> 38:26.250
Describe it exactly.

38:26.333 --> 38:28.541
Like a nightmare, but it's a smell.

38:28.625 --> 38:29.750
I can taste it.

38:30.625 --> 38:31.833
Where?

38:32.625 --> 38:33.916
Everywhere.

38:45.125 --> 38:47.291
We're in a Root Snake den.

38:47.791 --> 38:50.958
No, no, no. Forget this. No. Not me.

38:53.083 --> 38:55.958
Listen, I don't like you,
and you think you don't like me--

38:56.041 --> 38:57.708
Keep it down. They're gonna hear us.

38:57.791 --> 39:02.166
Ugh. Root Snakes are really
hard of hearing. They feel vibrations.

39:04.833 --> 39:06.000
Okay.

39:06.083 --> 39:09.625
Here's the plan.
We're gonna have to walk across the roots.

39:09.708 --> 39:13.875
Um, speaking of hard of hearing.
I just said they feel vibrations,

39:13.958 --> 39:17.250
and the roots and the snakes
look identical. So, no, no.

39:17.333 --> 39:20.291
That's not gonna work.
I'm gonna come up with another plan.

39:20.375 --> 39:24.583
Cut the bossy routine for one second
and listen to me.

39:24.666 --> 39:27.208
You gotta use your Pookoo nose.

39:27.291 --> 39:30.041
Pookoo can see smells.

39:30.750 --> 39:33.125
Pookoo can see smells?

39:33.708 --> 39:37.416
Okay, okay, first, close your eyes.

39:37.500 --> 39:39.458
Close my eyes in a snake den?

39:39.541 --> 39:44.291
Listen, no smell matters
except a stench right in front of you.

39:47.666 --> 39:51.333
Oh, wow! You can see smells!

39:51.833 --> 39:54.583
Ah, it's like having eyeballs
in your nose!

39:54.666 --> 39:57.208
-Can we stay on task, please?
-Oh, right.

39:59.166 --> 40:01.083
-Root.
-Our lives depend on it.

40:01.166 --> 40:03.083
Are you absolutely sure?

40:03.166 --> 40:04.916
Oh, yeah, I'm sure.

40:05.000 --> 40:07.541
That's a root. Trust me on this.

40:18.166 --> 40:21.291
Okay, okay, I've got this.

40:22.583 --> 40:24.666
I can see that's a…

40:25.541 --> 40:27.583
-Root Snake.
-Are you saying root or snake?

40:27.666 --> 40:29.666
I am saying Root Snake.

40:29.750 --> 40:31.625
See? The emphasis is on "snake."

40:31.708 --> 40:33.958
When it's a "root,"
I put the emphasis on "root."

40:34.041 --> 40:38.208
Just say "root" or "snake."
"Root" or "snake."

40:38.291 --> 40:40.541
Okay, snake.

40:40.625 --> 40:42.458
Good. Keep sniffing.

40:43.625 --> 40:45.291
Okay, root. Go.

40:48.041 --> 40:50.708
Root, root. Good, good.

40:51.416 --> 40:54.083
Snake, definitely a snake.

40:55.416 --> 40:57.208
Try that big one on the right.

40:59.041 --> 41:00.125
Root.

41:00.750 --> 41:02.416
Root. Step left.

41:02.500 --> 41:03.500
No, snake!

41:04.541 --> 41:06.583
This way. This way. Uh, stop.

41:07.958 --> 41:09.333
Big step to your right.

41:09.416 --> 41:11.083
There we go. Root.

41:11.583 --> 41:14.125
Snake. Right.

41:14.875 --> 41:17.750
Left. Snake, snake. That way.

41:18.250 --> 41:22.041
Okay, root, root. Good.
Keep going ahead. Yep, yep, yep.

41:22.125 --> 41:23.166
Almost there.

41:23.250 --> 41:26.000
We're doing it. Well, mostly I'm doing it.

41:30.500 --> 41:31.500
Hmm.

41:38.875 --> 41:39.875
Supper.

41:39.958 --> 41:41.375
Savory.

41:41.458 --> 41:42.791
Starving.

41:43.541 --> 41:44.958
That's not good.

41:45.041 --> 41:46.291
Run.

42:00.291 --> 42:01.625
Savory!

42:01.708 --> 42:04.416
-Stuck.
-Sic 'em.

42:04.500 --> 42:08.791
I think we can take 'em.
I'll go for the eyes, you wrestle 'em.

42:08.875 --> 42:11.750
Are you nuts? No. You have to fly!

42:11.833 --> 42:13.791
I told you! I don't fly!

42:16.250 --> 42:18.291
We're gonna die!

42:18.375 --> 42:21.083
Don't panic!
Focus on your lift, drag, and thrust!

42:21.166 --> 42:23.416
Feel the rising air flowing
through your feathers!

42:23.500 --> 42:24.958
What feathers? These?

42:25.041 --> 42:27.791
No, those are your primaries!
I'm talking about your axials!

42:27.875 --> 42:30.125
-Axi-what?
-Okay, Ollie. Flap or splat!

42:30.208 --> 42:31.666
-Splat?!
-No, flap!

42:31.750 --> 42:34.250
It's how every Javan learns to fly.
Trust me on this!

42:34.333 --> 42:37.125
-I'm scared, Ivy!
-Then trust yourself!

42:37.875 --> 42:39.583
Flap, Ollie, flap!

42:50.458 --> 42:52.125
Ollie, you're flying.

42:52.208 --> 42:54.083
Am I? I… I am?

42:54.166 --> 42:56.000
-I am!
-Watch it!

42:57.291 --> 42:58.333
Careful there!

43:00.500 --> 43:01.541
That's it.

43:02.083 --> 43:05.375
Yeah! You're a natural.

43:05.458 --> 43:08.875
Whoo! This is great. This feels amazing!

43:19.791 --> 43:22.750
Mmm, let's not attempt a flyby.

43:22.833 --> 43:27.041
What was that? A flyby? Comin' right up!

43:27.125 --> 43:29.666
Whoa! Careful.

43:33.958 --> 43:35.541
Whoa, what's this?

43:35.625 --> 43:38.291
It's an updraft. Just ride it.

43:59.458 --> 44:02.416
Okay, Ollie. You can take us down now.

44:02.500 --> 44:04.541
Did you just say "take us down"?

44:05.125 --> 44:06.166
Ollie…

44:06.666 --> 44:09.375
Ollie!

44:09.458 --> 44:11.458
Whoo-hoo!

44:42.208 --> 44:43.416
Whoo!

44:46.625 --> 44:48.875
Why didn't you tell me
about flying sooner?

44:48.958 --> 44:51.833
Um, I did. Several times.

44:51.916 --> 44:54.291
Well, you obviously
didn't explain it very well

44:54.375 --> 44:56.500
because if you had,
I would have understood it.

45:01.541 --> 45:03.708
Thanks. You know, for…

45:04.708 --> 45:06.666
-For pushing me back there.
-Oh!

45:08.125 --> 45:09.250
You're welcome.

45:10.500 --> 45:14.041
No one's ever thanked me
for being pushy before.

45:17.666 --> 45:20.333
Okay. The Great Waterfall's
gotta be around here somewhere.

45:20.416 --> 45:21.833
Let's try for it.

45:21.916 --> 45:23.500
Mmm, we're losing light,

45:23.583 --> 45:25.166
and it's too foggy.

45:25.250 --> 45:26.583
We'll find it in the morning.

45:28.250 --> 45:30.500
Ooh, I know that sound.

45:30.583 --> 45:32.375
Somebody's hungry.

45:33.000 --> 45:34.208
-I'm fine.
-Mm-hmm.

45:34.291 --> 45:35.291
Sure.

45:36.458 --> 45:38.708
Javan need to eat throughout the day.

45:39.458 --> 45:42.833
So, by my estimate,
you're barely hanging on.

45:43.958 --> 45:46.541
Here. Brush root. Helps fight the hunger.

45:48.541 --> 45:49.500
Mmm.

45:49.583 --> 45:51.083
Ugh!

45:51.166 --> 45:53.750
You'll get used to it…
in a couple of years.

45:53.833 --> 45:55.583
I can't… You…

45:55.666 --> 45:57.583
You choose to eat this?

45:57.666 --> 46:00.208
The Javan owe their lives to that stuff.

46:01.666 --> 46:04.250
When the Dzo left,
we lost our food source.

46:05.208 --> 46:08.291
The brush root kept the hunger down,
but only for so long.

46:10.208 --> 46:11.791
The Javan almost starved.

46:13.375 --> 46:16.208
I didn't know that.

46:18.458 --> 46:20.041
We lost so many.

46:21.583 --> 46:23.875
Friends, cousins,

46:24.666 --> 46:26.750
aunts, uncles.

46:32.125 --> 46:33.500
My mom and dad.

46:41.875 --> 46:44.958
I was the oldest, so, um…

46:45.875 --> 46:50.250
It was on me to find food for my sisters
so they didn't starve.

46:50.791 --> 46:53.625
Not that they appreciate it
for a second, of course.

46:54.375 --> 46:57.291
They just think of me
as a bossy, annoying big sis.

46:59.583 --> 47:01.541
But if I don't look out for them,

47:02.458 --> 47:03.541
who will?

47:08.166 --> 47:12.166
That sounds like a… heavy burden.

47:19.458 --> 47:20.458
Yeah.

47:22.500 --> 47:25.041
Thank goodness I found the piplets.

47:25.125 --> 47:26.833
They really saved us.

47:28.208 --> 47:29.458
You what?

47:29.541 --> 47:31.541
I discovered our new food source.

47:31.625 --> 47:32.916
It was years ago.

47:33.000 --> 47:36.958
Come to think of it,
that was the first time I met a Pookoo.

47:37.041 --> 47:40.250
I didn't know what it was called,
but there was this little guy

47:40.333 --> 47:43.291
who showed me
how to open the piplet seeds.

47:44.333 --> 47:45.333
Huh.

47:46.750 --> 47:48.375
You look exhausted.

47:48.458 --> 47:51.375
I think it's time to hit the hay.

47:52.000 --> 47:53.250
Good night, Ollie.

47:53.916 --> 47:56.458
Oh, and Javan sleep upside down.

47:57.416 --> 47:58.583
Just kidding!

48:13.916 --> 48:16.041
Um, Ollie?

48:17.208 --> 48:18.208
Ollie!

48:19.916 --> 48:21.458
The Great Waterfall!

48:26.875 --> 48:29.708
Look! There's the Dzo!

48:39.958 --> 48:42.000
Dad, I'm hungry.

48:42.083 --> 48:44.416
I know. You remind me every minute.

48:44.500 --> 48:47.416
Because I'm hungry!

48:47.500 --> 48:51.083
Wolves! It's a wolf den.

48:54.291 --> 48:55.375
Hey, guys!

48:55.458 --> 48:58.916
Oh, thank goodness. I didn't get
a chance to tell you before, but--

48:59.000 --> 49:02.833
Yeah, the wolf den.
Yeah, pretty important, the wolf den.

49:02.916 --> 49:04.083
There's no way in.

49:04.166 --> 49:07.583
I have a way to get you in.
Don't worry. I'm gonna distract them.

49:07.666 --> 49:11.291
Wait, wait. You'd do that for us?

49:11.375 --> 49:15.166
Well… you guys are my only friends.

49:15.250 --> 49:19.750
And when you change back,
I won't have any friends anymore, so…

49:22.416 --> 49:24.458
So I was hoping maybe you could…

49:24.541 --> 49:25.583
Get you a pod!

49:25.666 --> 49:27.250
You could become a Javan.

49:27.916 --> 49:31.041
Or a Pookoo.
They've got a killer schnoz.

49:31.125 --> 49:33.666
Oh… A Pookoo…

49:33.750 --> 49:36.708
Aw, ah! That would be great!

49:36.791 --> 49:38.958
We are getting you a pod, Boogle.

49:39.041 --> 49:40.125
That's a promise.

49:40.208 --> 49:43.083
Thank you. Okay, now hurry.
You won't have much time.

49:43.166 --> 49:45.916
But wait. How are you gonna distract
the wolves?

49:46.000 --> 49:48.333
I'm gonna be their lunch.

50:01.125 --> 50:04.625
That is one big fish.

50:04.708 --> 50:06.583
I call dibs on the head.

50:19.250 --> 50:21.750
Dad, you're letting it get away!

50:27.791 --> 50:29.750
The pods! The pods!

50:31.541 --> 50:34.250
But there's only one.

50:34.333 --> 50:37.375
No, there's gotta be more.
The Boogle said there are plenty of 'em.

50:38.458 --> 50:40.583
We don't have much time.
I'll just take it.

50:40.666 --> 50:43.041
Hey. Wait, wait, wait. Why?

50:43.125 --> 50:44.125
I'll be a Javan again.

50:44.208 --> 50:46.541
We can fly around together
and find another one.

50:50.416 --> 50:52.250
What? You don't trust me?

50:54.750 --> 50:56.541
You don't trust me?

50:58.250 --> 50:59.291
Ouch.

50:59.375 --> 51:02.791
Okay. Well, my community is relying on me.

51:02.875 --> 51:04.625
Oh, and mine isn't?

51:04.708 --> 51:07.750
Come on. It's not the same,
not even by a long shot.

51:07.833 --> 51:09.083
I'll have you know,

51:09.166 --> 51:11.875
it's my job to make sure
the Javan fatten up for the winter.

51:11.958 --> 51:13.000
Fatten up?

51:13.083 --> 51:14.958
Yes, and our piplets are running low.

51:15.041 --> 51:16.333
Your piplets?

51:16.416 --> 51:18.708
-Yes.
-You mean the ones you took from me?

51:18.791 --> 51:22.208
What? I have never taken anything
from you.

51:22.291 --> 51:25.208
You really don't remember, do you?

51:25.291 --> 51:28.208
Remember what?
Ollie, what are you talking about?

51:28.291 --> 51:31.708
The little Pookoo
who taught you how to open the piplets?

51:32.708 --> 51:34.750
That was me.

51:37.250 --> 51:39.416
You ate everything,
you ran us underground,

51:39.500 --> 51:41.333
and now we live off your scraps.

51:41.416 --> 51:43.625
My dad told me outsiders
weren't to be trusted,

51:43.708 --> 51:45.875
but I didn't listen. I never listen!

51:45.958 --> 51:47.208
And it's all my fault

51:47.291 --> 51:50.666
because I was so gullible
and naive and stupid!

51:50.750 --> 51:53.666
We're not gonna survive the winter.
Do you understand that?

51:54.250 --> 51:55.708
We're gonna starve.

51:59.333 --> 52:00.333
I…

52:05.791 --> 52:07.958
It's all my fault.

52:12.541 --> 52:13.541
You know…

52:14.458 --> 52:15.916
My own father…

52:16.625 --> 52:19.791
He won't even look me in the eye.

52:22.541 --> 52:24.166
And it's all because

52:25.166 --> 52:26.916
I trusted you.

52:37.666 --> 52:38.750
Boogle!

52:38.833 --> 52:40.750
-Help, Boogle!
-Boogle! Help!

52:40.833 --> 52:43.416
Boogle! Boogle!

52:52.375 --> 52:53.375
Help!

52:54.750 --> 52:55.708
Help!

52:57.750 --> 52:58.750
Ollie?!

52:58.833 --> 53:00.333
And Nobody?

53:01.000 --> 53:03.625
You're Boogles? What happened?

53:04.208 --> 53:06.875
Uh, there was only one pod,

53:06.958 --> 53:10.375
and we said "Boogle"
just before we touched it.

53:11.208 --> 53:15.625
Now that I think about it, I said "Pookoo"
before I touched the other pod.

53:15.708 --> 53:17.583
That must be how the pods work.

53:17.666 --> 53:19.583
You become whatever you say.

53:19.666 --> 53:21.875
Great. That'll help us
when we go back in time

53:21.958 --> 53:23.500
and do this over again.

53:24.500 --> 53:26.083
Ivy, we're fish.

53:26.166 --> 53:30.250
Thanks to you, I'm even further away
from getting home and saving my village.

53:30.333 --> 53:31.958
-Ollie, listen--
-Look.

53:32.041 --> 53:33.541
You're a Javan.

53:33.625 --> 53:34.625
I'm a Pookoo.

53:35.291 --> 53:37.416
We were always meant to be separate.

53:40.458 --> 53:42.333
This is where we say goodbye.

53:43.208 --> 53:44.291
So…

53:49.708 --> 53:52.375
Bye, Ollie! I'll miss you!

53:52.458 --> 53:54.291
Have a great life as a Boogle!

53:54.375 --> 53:57.208
I'll just tell Ivy
about the other pods, then.

53:57.291 --> 53:59.458
There's a whole bunch of 'em!

53:59.541 --> 54:01.333
So long, Ollie!

54:01.416 --> 54:04.791
I'll always remember you!

54:20.083 --> 54:22.125
Hey, I don't mean to pry,

54:22.625 --> 54:25.375
but you two don't seem
to be getting along too well.

54:25.458 --> 54:27.000
Yeah. It is what it is.

54:27.083 --> 54:29.333
These pods, see,

54:29.416 --> 54:32.500
they're at the top of Scary Rock Falls.

54:32.583 --> 54:35.000
I'm afraid to even say the words.

54:35.083 --> 54:36.791
Scariest place in the Valley.

54:36.875 --> 54:39.666
We need to work together
to make it up there,

54:39.750 --> 54:42.958
so you two need to make up quick, okay?

54:48.958 --> 54:52.916
Okay. I'll let you two in on
a little secret.

54:53.000 --> 54:57.750
You see me, and you probably think,
"Wow, Boogle has it all."

54:57.833 --> 55:01.750
Brains, looks, charm, brains.

55:02.291 --> 55:03.625
But the truth is,

55:04.291 --> 55:05.916
Boogle doesn't have it all.

55:07.041 --> 55:13.750
I spent my whole life wandering this lake,
knowing something was missing.

55:15.750 --> 55:17.666
Then I realized what it was.

55:22.541 --> 55:23.958
I was all alone.

55:27.875 --> 55:32.208
And I can tell you,
when you're alone for so long…

55:34.041 --> 55:39.125
you go into some dark, dark places.

55:42.541 --> 55:44.083
What I mean is,

55:44.166 --> 55:50.250
it makes you really appreciate
why we need each other.

56:08.750 --> 56:09.750
Ollie.

56:10.625 --> 56:11.666
I am…

56:14.125 --> 56:18.666
When we were kids,
you were the first Pookoo I'd ever met.

56:19.333 --> 56:21.375
My sisters hadn't eaten in days.

56:22.916 --> 56:24.416
And I was scared.

56:25.458 --> 56:28.333
But something about you made me trust you.

56:29.250 --> 56:30.750
You were kind to me.

56:31.250 --> 56:33.833
You showed me how to eat the piplets.

56:34.458 --> 56:35.875
And then you were gone.

56:37.750 --> 56:39.708
I never knew where you went.

56:40.583 --> 56:45.125
But… I never forgot you.

56:47.000 --> 56:48.291
And, Ollie…

56:49.791 --> 56:52.458
I never knew how much I hurt you.

56:54.000 --> 56:57.375
I am so, so sorry.

57:01.291 --> 57:02.333
Look!

57:02.416 --> 57:04.541
We are here!

57:07.458 --> 57:10.750
Scary Rock Falls.

57:13.458 --> 57:15.708
Pods! Tons of pods!

57:15.791 --> 57:17.791
I'm going for it! I'm going for it!

57:27.791 --> 57:29.500
Yeah, tried that.

57:29.583 --> 57:32.291
The waterfall's too strong
for a single Boogle,

57:32.375 --> 57:34.833
but not for thriple Boogle.

57:34.916 --> 57:36.791
Form Megafish!

57:36.875 --> 57:39.083
-Megafish?
-Megafish. Right.

57:39.166 --> 57:42.541
Lock fins and swim together. Megafish!

57:42.625 --> 57:44.458
Swim as one!

57:56.750 --> 57:59.583
-Whoo!
-All right. One down. Two to go.

57:59.666 --> 58:00.833
Yeah, baby!

58:07.625 --> 58:09.791
What am I seeing? What is this?

58:13.208 --> 58:14.208
Fish?

58:14.291 --> 58:15.916
-Fish?
-Fish.

58:16.000 --> 58:18.583
Fish?

58:18.666 --> 58:19.708
What are those?

58:19.791 --> 58:22.583
Those? Those are the scary rocks.

58:23.666 --> 58:25.333
Fish!

58:43.500 --> 58:44.916
Reform Megafish!

59:02.416 --> 59:03.625
Almost there!

59:11.666 --> 59:14.500
Okay, now what do we do?
Come on, now, anybody.

59:18.166 --> 59:20.333
Ah, Dad!

59:25.958 --> 59:29.125
Now's our chance.

59:31.208 --> 59:33.625
What are we waiting for? Let's go!

59:34.125 --> 59:36.250
The pup! Grab my tail!

01:00:19.833 --> 01:00:21.000
-Whoo!
-Yes!

01:00:21.083 --> 01:00:23.916
We made it.
How did you even do all of that?

01:00:24.000 --> 01:00:26.666
Me? You had moves back there.

01:00:26.750 --> 01:00:28.250
You're a natural.

01:00:32.125 --> 01:00:33.125
You hear that?

01:00:33.625 --> 01:00:34.708
The Dzo.

01:00:36.125 --> 01:00:37.250
That's them.

01:00:40.708 --> 01:00:43.333
How about this? Together, on three.

01:00:43.416 --> 01:00:46.000
-One, two, three!
-One, two, three!

01:00:46.083 --> 01:00:47.541
-Pookoo!
-Javan!

01:00:48.666 --> 01:00:51.541
-Yeah! Thank you!
-Yes! I'm back!

01:00:51.625 --> 01:00:53.125
I'm back, baby!

01:00:54.166 --> 01:00:55.291
Hey, guys!

01:00:55.375 --> 01:00:58.875
Hey, Boogle. What are you gonna become?

01:00:58.958 --> 01:01:01.000
I was just trying to decide that.

01:01:01.083 --> 01:01:04.458
A Pookoo, a Javan,
a Pinecone Hedgehog, or…

01:01:04.541 --> 01:01:06.458
Or, wait. I know.

01:01:06.541 --> 01:01:08.791
Maybe I could just become the…

01:01:09.666 --> 01:01:11.208
Firewolf!

01:01:14.750 --> 01:01:15.750
Boogle?

01:01:18.208 --> 01:01:20.291
There was never Boogle.

01:01:29.166 --> 01:01:31.500
There was only ever

01:01:32.500 --> 01:01:33.625
me.

01:01:34.125 --> 01:01:35.125
The Tale.

01:01:35.916 --> 01:01:38.416
You're the one… You tore the Valley apart.

01:01:38.500 --> 01:01:41.750
You created the dam.
You drove the Dzo out.

01:01:41.833 --> 01:01:44.666
Yes, yes, and yes.

01:01:44.750 --> 01:01:47.000
I'm good. What can I say?

01:01:47.083 --> 01:01:48.666
But why? You ruined everything.

01:01:48.750 --> 01:01:51.750
There was so much peace here,
and you destroyed it.

01:01:51.833 --> 01:01:54.583
-You caused so much pain.
-What about my pain?!

01:01:55.083 --> 01:01:57.583
I was the runt of my litter,

01:01:57.666 --> 01:01:59.958
so my pack tossed me aside to die,

01:02:00.041 --> 01:02:04.500
and none of the other creatures
wanted me around.

01:02:04.583 --> 01:02:09.291
So I promised myself that one day
I would burn the Valley down

01:02:09.375 --> 01:02:13.333
and those who survived
would bow down to me.

01:02:14.000 --> 01:02:15.583
I ruled this place

01:02:15.666 --> 01:02:19.458
until those tree monsters
sent one last pod

01:02:19.541 --> 01:02:22.958
and trapped me in that hideous fish body.

01:02:23.833 --> 01:02:24.833
The pods.

01:02:24.916 --> 01:02:28.291
I waited ages for someone to come along.

01:02:28.375 --> 01:02:31.958
Some gullible, trusting fool like you!

01:02:32.791 --> 01:02:36.708
"Oh, Ollie. You'd do that for me? Wow."

01:02:36.791 --> 01:02:38.208
"You're my best friend."

01:02:42.500 --> 01:02:44.666
Did you even think about any of this?

01:02:44.750 --> 01:02:47.875
You thought that pack of puny Tree Wolves

01:02:47.958 --> 01:02:49.791
were Firewolves?

01:02:53.750 --> 01:02:54.791
Ivy!

01:02:55.291 --> 01:02:57.333
No, no, no, no, no! Ivy! Ivy!

01:02:57.416 --> 01:02:59.791
"Ivy! Ivy!"

01:02:59.875 --> 01:03:03.208
What are you crying about?
You wanted to get rid of her, didn't you?

01:03:04.208 --> 01:03:06.041
You think she's your friend?

01:03:06.625 --> 01:03:09.708
There are no friends in the Valley.

01:03:12.041 --> 01:03:18.666
It's time the Valley
was ruled by fear again.

01:03:25.750 --> 01:03:26.750
Ollie.

01:03:30.375 --> 01:03:32.166
He's wrong about you.

01:03:33.625 --> 01:03:34.625
Keep

01:03:35.333 --> 01:03:36.833
your heart

01:03:37.416 --> 01:03:38.541
open.

01:03:39.166 --> 01:03:42.000
No, no, no, no, no, no! Ivy! Ivy!

01:03:42.958 --> 01:03:44.041
No.

01:03:47.250 --> 01:03:49.166
I'm gonna get you to Javan Rock.

01:05:02.541 --> 01:05:03.541
Ivy?

01:05:05.333 --> 01:05:07.375
Help her.

01:05:16.708 --> 01:05:18.541
Ivy! Ivy!

01:05:19.041 --> 01:05:21.791
Where's Ivy?

01:05:21.875 --> 01:05:23.875
Oh, I'm sorry, love.

01:05:23.958 --> 01:05:26.291
She's… gone.

01:05:31.500 --> 01:05:32.666
Ivy…

01:05:34.375 --> 01:05:35.458
No.

01:05:38.375 --> 01:05:39.375
No.

01:05:45.500 --> 01:05:47.166
I'm so sorry.

01:05:49.583 --> 01:05:50.583
You were…

01:05:51.875 --> 01:05:53.166
the best friend…

01:05:55.125 --> 01:05:56.291
I ever had.

01:06:00.416 --> 01:06:01.750
There, there.

01:06:02.375 --> 01:06:06.250
Don't stop saying
all those nice things about me.

01:06:06.333 --> 01:06:09.791
How could you be here if she…
But she said you were gone.

01:06:09.875 --> 01:06:12.416
Gone to get you some food.

01:06:21.083 --> 01:06:22.625
I was right, you know.

01:06:23.291 --> 01:06:25.583
You still are that kind little Pookoo.

01:06:31.750 --> 01:06:34.791
Yeah, well, that kind little Pookoo…

01:06:36.125 --> 01:06:38.208
always seems to mess everything up.

01:06:44.416 --> 01:06:46.541
Let me show you something.

01:07:04.750 --> 01:07:05.750
Boo!

01:07:07.708 --> 01:07:08.791
Boo!

01:07:10.291 --> 01:07:11.291
Boo!

01:07:15.875 --> 01:07:19.250
Hey, you boys hear
about my brother's nest? Water damage.

01:07:19.333 --> 01:07:21.916
-Me grandson could help.
-Yeah?

01:07:22.000 --> 01:07:24.458
Oh, yeah. He's good at fixing stuff.

01:07:24.541 --> 01:07:26.541
Good at breaking it too!

01:07:27.125 --> 01:07:31.750
Flap or splat!
Flap or splat! Flap or splat!

01:07:35.083 --> 01:07:36.208
Flap or splat!

01:07:36.291 --> 01:07:38.541
Ooh!

01:07:38.625 --> 01:07:40.000
He splatted!

01:07:40.083 --> 01:07:41.291
I'm okay.

01:07:44.166 --> 01:07:49.625
I know this won't change the hurt
we, and I, caused your community.

01:07:50.250 --> 01:07:52.791
And for that, I am truly sorry.

01:07:53.458 --> 01:07:55.166
I want you to know,

01:07:55.250 --> 01:07:57.666
not everything you do turns out bad.

01:07:57.750 --> 01:08:00.833
All of their parents
were saved by the piplets

01:08:00.916 --> 01:08:03.083
that you showed me how to eat.

01:08:06.333 --> 01:08:09.041
None of them would be here without you.

01:08:13.875 --> 01:08:14.875
Thank you.

01:08:16.416 --> 01:08:18.291
That's him! That's Ollie!

01:08:20.708 --> 01:08:22.791
-He's so cute!
-Such a big nose!

01:08:22.875 --> 01:08:24.583
Why's he so fluffy?

01:08:24.666 --> 01:08:27.500
How did he fly up here
with such small wings?

01:08:27.583 --> 01:08:30.250
Ah, I can't fly, as a Pookoo.

01:08:31.583 --> 01:08:34.375
He can talk!

01:08:34.458 --> 01:08:36.875
Hi, Dung Baby! Remember us?

01:08:36.958 --> 01:08:39.625
-We covered you in dung.
-Yeah, I remember.

01:08:41.125 --> 01:08:43.208
But thank you. You saved me.

01:08:44.875 --> 01:08:46.291
Look! It's snowing!

01:08:46.375 --> 01:08:48.458
-It's snowing!
-I love snow!

01:08:48.541 --> 01:08:50.041
It's snowing! Wow!

01:08:50.125 --> 01:08:52.250
-It's snowing!
-Yes! No school!

01:08:52.333 --> 01:08:53.250
It's snowing!

01:08:53.333 --> 01:08:54.916
This isn't snow.

01:09:01.375 --> 01:09:02.666
Firewolf.

01:09:02.750 --> 01:09:05.166
The fire is spreading fast.

01:09:05.250 --> 01:09:08.458
The skies aren't safe.
Get everyone to their nests!

01:09:08.541 --> 01:09:10.125
We need to help the Valley.

01:09:10.208 --> 01:09:13.041
Wait! Everyone stop!

01:09:13.125 --> 01:09:14.708
We have to help.

01:09:14.791 --> 01:09:17.833
It's too dangerous.
We have to look after our own.

01:09:17.916 --> 01:09:19.708
Everyone, listen up!

01:09:20.333 --> 01:09:25.208
Now, my big sister may be bossy
and annoying and overbearing…

01:09:25.291 --> 01:09:27.333
Some might actually even say tyrannical--

01:09:27.416 --> 01:09:28.458
Hold on!

01:09:28.541 --> 01:09:29.541
I'm talking.

01:09:29.625 --> 01:09:31.791
Not only does she interrupt,
she talks too much.

01:09:31.875 --> 01:09:33.875
Also, her plume is annoyingly big.

01:09:33.958 --> 01:09:36.833
These are all things
we obviously agree on. But…

01:09:37.333 --> 01:09:41.125
She has always risked herself
to take care of us.

01:09:42.000 --> 01:09:44.208
And we wouldn't be here without her.

01:09:46.708 --> 01:09:49.708
She thinks I don't know that, but I do.

01:09:49.791 --> 01:09:54.291
Look, she may not always be right,
but she is definitely right about this.

01:09:54.375 --> 01:09:55.916
The Valley needs our help.

01:09:56.000 --> 01:09:58.500
Violet's right about Ivy being right.

01:10:41.833 --> 01:10:44.666
All these creatures! They're trapped!

01:10:44.750 --> 01:10:47.833
Let's help them out.
We can lead them to the shore.

01:10:47.916 --> 01:10:50.541
That is a great idea, Violet.

01:10:50.625 --> 01:10:51.708
We'll do the same.

01:11:06.750 --> 01:11:08.208
Stay close!

01:11:14.666 --> 01:11:16.791
It's okay. We're here to help.

01:11:38.041 --> 01:11:39.041
Uh…

01:11:40.791 --> 01:11:43.666
Pookoo Island.
It's the only safe place left.

01:11:43.750 --> 01:11:45.208
How are we gonna get them there?

01:11:58.208 --> 01:12:00.791
Thank you for saving my son.

01:12:01.916 --> 01:12:03.166
What do you say?

01:12:03.250 --> 01:12:04.333
Thank you!

01:12:06.875 --> 01:12:08.250
We can help.

01:12:29.041 --> 01:12:33.083
All aboard!
No time for lollygagging! No panic!

01:12:33.166 --> 01:12:35.000
My hero!

01:12:35.083 --> 01:12:36.750
Let's move out!

01:13:04.083 --> 01:13:06.583
-Ollie?
-He's alive?

01:13:07.083 --> 01:13:09.125
Mom! Dad! I need your help!

01:13:09.625 --> 01:13:10.916
Ollie!

01:13:25.333 --> 01:13:26.541
No!

01:13:34.250 --> 01:13:35.625
Ivy!

01:13:39.333 --> 01:13:41.875
Watch out! Get away from those things!

01:13:41.958 --> 01:13:46.000
Dad, listen to me. It's not an attack.
These are the creatures of the Valley.

01:13:46.083 --> 01:13:48.416
They don't have anywhere else to go.
They need help.

01:13:50.625 --> 01:13:51.791
Dad.

01:13:52.291 --> 01:13:53.541
They need our help.

01:13:54.041 --> 01:13:56.125
Help me bring them onto the island.

01:13:56.208 --> 01:13:58.666
We can't do that, Ollie.

01:13:58.750 --> 01:14:02.416
Never trust anything but a Pookoo.
You know this.

01:14:02.500 --> 01:14:05.625
No, Dad, the Tale. It's all true.

01:14:05.708 --> 01:14:08.041
The Dzo, the Firewolf, the pods.

01:14:08.125 --> 01:14:11.041
I've used those pods
to become the creatures of the Valley,

01:14:11.125 --> 01:14:12.625
and I've learned something.

01:14:18.375 --> 01:14:19.791
We're stronger

01:14:20.708 --> 01:14:21.916
together.

01:14:23.416 --> 01:14:25.500
Dad, I know you're scared.

01:14:26.666 --> 01:14:28.958
But we have to trust each other.

01:15:20.000 --> 01:15:21.250
Ollie!

01:15:22.666 --> 01:15:26.541
Ollie!

01:15:40.083 --> 01:15:41.875
We don't have much time.

01:15:42.666 --> 01:15:43.791
Follow me.

01:15:48.000 --> 01:15:50.625
-What's the plan?
-The Firewolf said it himself.

01:15:50.708 --> 01:15:54.083
The Dzo set the pod to trap him once.
Maybe we can do it again.

01:15:57.791 --> 01:15:59.250
Are you sure about this?

01:15:59.833 --> 01:16:00.875
Nope.

01:16:13.208 --> 01:16:15.916
Dzo, are you out there?

01:16:16.000 --> 01:16:17.250
Can you hear me?

01:16:22.916 --> 01:16:24.583
Ollie, hurry!

01:16:25.875 --> 01:16:29.291
All I need is one more pod.
Can you send me one more pod?

01:16:29.375 --> 01:16:32.625
Please, please, please.
The Valley needs your help.

01:16:37.291 --> 01:16:38.458
Please.

01:17:01.375 --> 01:17:02.416
Dzo.

01:17:20.708 --> 01:17:22.291
The Dzo.

01:17:22.791 --> 01:17:24.166
It can't be.

01:17:26.208 --> 01:17:28.458
Okay, Ollie, we've got this.

01:17:30.125 --> 01:17:31.125
Ollie?

01:17:31.208 --> 01:17:32.833
That's our son.

01:17:52.041 --> 01:17:53.583
Stay away from them.

01:17:54.208 --> 01:17:56.666
Ollie, you found another pod.

01:17:56.750 --> 01:17:59.416
Oh, you noticed.

01:18:28.333 --> 01:18:30.166
Gullible little Firewolf.

01:18:30.958 --> 01:18:32.375
I liked you better as a…

01:18:32.458 --> 01:18:33.416
Boogle!

01:18:40.041 --> 01:18:44.000
You thought I wouldn't be ready
for the same pathetic trap.

01:18:44.083 --> 01:18:46.541
Who's the gullible one now?

01:19:19.958 --> 01:19:22.416
Ollie, Ollie, Ollie…

01:19:23.166 --> 01:19:25.708
What are you gonna do now?

01:19:25.791 --> 01:19:29.291
You can't jump in the water
because it's too deep,

01:19:29.375 --> 01:19:31.083
and Dzos sink.

01:19:31.166 --> 01:19:32.875
Watch your step, Ollie!

01:19:39.708 --> 01:19:41.125
You think you're a Dzo?

01:19:41.208 --> 01:19:45.041
Restoring peace and harmony to the Valley.

01:19:45.125 --> 01:19:49.666
You're just an angry little rat
fighting in vain for what's yours.

01:19:51.875 --> 01:19:55.291
Only this time, it's your life.

01:19:58.250 --> 01:20:01.208
This is my valley now.

01:20:03.375 --> 01:20:04.375
What?

01:20:17.416 --> 01:20:18.791
No.

01:20:18.875 --> 01:20:20.250
It's our valley.

01:20:25.833 --> 01:20:26.833
No.

01:20:27.916 --> 01:20:30.333
No, no, no. No.

01:20:30.416 --> 01:20:32.125
What are you doing? Stop.

01:20:32.625 --> 01:20:34.000
You have to stop.

01:20:34.708 --> 01:20:37.333
Hey. Trust me on this.

01:20:43.958 --> 01:20:46.500
No!

01:21:03.416 --> 01:21:05.083
Ollie!

01:21:19.666 --> 01:21:20.916
Ollie!

01:21:22.666 --> 01:21:23.708
Ollie!

01:21:25.583 --> 01:21:26.708
Ollie!

01:21:28.041 --> 01:21:29.666
Ollie!

01:25:06.041 --> 01:25:08.416
Ollie! Ollie!

01:25:09.666 --> 01:25:10.875
You're alive!

01:25:10.958 --> 01:25:14.125
Ah! I thought you were gone forever!

01:25:14.208 --> 01:25:16.958
Where… How did you… I…

01:25:17.583 --> 01:25:19.541
The Dzo. They found me.

01:25:20.250 --> 01:25:24.125
You know, they have
these things called, uh, magic pods.
